/-!
From now on we assume that `f` approximates an invertible continuous linear map `f : E ‚âÉL[ùïú] F`.

We also assume that either `E = {0}`, or `c < ‚Äñf'‚Åª¬π‚Äñ‚Åª¬π`. We use `N` as an abbreviation for `‚Äñf'‚Åª¬π‚Äñ`.
